Cell.Text: [S] G|OK, I guess I'll wait a while but I'm not waiting forever.
[S] G|OK I'll be here... maybe.
[S] G|Fine... let me get killed. Oh don't worry I can handle myself.
[S] G|I'll just sit here like a good doggie.
[S] G|Why do you get to have all the fun?
[S] G|I hope I don't get plundered by bandits... Unless they happen to be good looking of course.
[S] G|I'll be here, unless I find someone better to stalk.
[S] G|Don't be too long. I hate having to entertain myself.
[S] G|Don't you dare forget and leave me here otherwise I am gone.
[S] G|Good, I needed a rest anyways.
[S] G|Wake me up when you get back.
[S] G|Don't take too long!
[S] G|Okay... okay...
[S] G|Don't take too long, I'll either be gone or asleep.
[S] G|OK I'll be here... maybe.
[S] G|It might be good to check the stables if I'm not here anymore... hehe
[S] G|You would leave your wife all on her own?
[S] G|If you don't come back for me, I will make sure that you never come back at all.
[S] G|Oh trust me you don't want to leave me for too long otherwise you will never hear the last of it.
[S] OK but next time you can carry my stuff.
[S] Well OK but only because it's you.
[S] OK but if I hurt my back you'll be carrying me.
[S] Yippee I love holding peoples junk.
[S] Do I have a choice? Well OK but you owe me.
[S] Oops, I dropped something... Just kidding.
[S] Uh oh, I hope that wasn't valuable... Haha You should have seen your face.
[S] OK, but don't push your luck.
[S] How about for a change you do something to... I mean for me.
[S] Are you sure you want to trust me with that?
[S] How about you take me instead... Damn it that came out wrong.
[S] Fine but don't take advantage of me... At least not in that way.
[S] I take it by trade you mean dump all your useless junk on me. Fine.
[S] Why must I hump all these stupid objects just to please you? I mean hump as in carrying stuff by the way not that kind. | Before your dirty mind gets any ideas.
[S] Do I get more booze?
[S] Yeaaaah... sure, some things.
[S] Aaahh, not too heavy right?
[S] Right now? OK, but don't complain if I move too slow!
[S] If it's jewelry, I won't complain.
[S] Sure... wait, what was the question?
[S] I may be your wife but I'm certainly not your slave.
[S] If it's a load of old junk then you will be sleeping on the floor tonight.
[S] This better be good otherwise I will be stopping all privileges if you know what I mean.
[S] OK I guess in a relationship you have to share responsibility but don't you start slacking off.
[S] All this marriage stuff better not be making you weak.

Node.Caption: JJSofiaDialogueTradeTopic: I would like to trade some things with you.

Cell.Text: [S] G|I'm gonna miss you... Well not really. OK maybe a little.
[S] G|OK but don't blame me when you get eaten by a sabrecat or mauled by a bear.
[S] G|Well OK but you better come and see me again.
[S] G|Are you breaking up with me? Oh well see you.
[S] G|OK but you'll be back... won't you?
[S] G|If you find somebody else I will hunt them down. Not really.
[S] G|But I was having so much fun. Maybe next time we'll have some real fun.
[S] G|I'll just find someone even better to hang around with then. Don't you get jealous.
[S] G|What's wrong with me? Am I not enough for you? OK, OK I understand.
[S] G|OK but I want to see more of you... much more.
G|HA... very funny.
G|That's a good one.
G|No no no, there's time for serious business later.
[S] G|You better be off to earn some more gold.
[S] G|You better not be seeing someone else behind my back.
[S] G|As your wife I have a right to go where I please... OK OK I'll give you a little space.

Node.Caption: JJSofiaDialoguePartWaysTopic: It's time for us to part ways

Cell.Text: [S] G|I knew you couldn't stay away from me.
[S] G|Anything to please you... Well maybe not anything.
[S] G|Why should I follow you? Actually, I can think of a few good reasons.
[S] G|OK let's go pick some flowers... just kidding, I want to go and kill something.
[S] G|You came back for me? I mean of course you did.
[S] G|I was kind of hoping you would come back.
[S] G|Thank goodness it's you. I thought you were a stalker... no offense.
[S] G|Well, I have nothing better to do I suppose.
[S] G|You've been thinking about me haven't you?
[S] G|You can take me anytime... Uh I mean you can take me with you... yeah.
[S] G|No. Why would I want to follow you? Haha I'm just kidding of course.
[S] G|I have been so bored. I never thought I'd want you so bad... Uh I mean want to see you.
[S] Are you saying you don't trust me? Fair point actually. I wouldn't trust me.
[S] Hmph. You're no fun.
[S] Is it because you're scared what I might do with it?
[S] I can't promise anything.
[S] Are you sure you want to do that now? I can barely hold a drink.
[S] Hmpf, you're no fun.
[S] I'll probably forget.
[S] If I fall, it's your fault!
[S] We are married yet you still keep things from me?
[S] Fine but if you keep anything good from me then I will keep something good from you. Understand?
[S] OK I guess you can still keep a few belongings but the gold is mine... I mean ours.
[S] We may be married but I guess some things will never change.

Cell.Text: [S] G|OK.
[S] G|You got it.
[S] G|I'll get right on it.
[S] G|No problem.
[S] G|I can do that.
[S] G|Is that all?
[S] G|Yes.
[S] G|Always glad to help.
[S] G|Just leave it to me.
